					<msContents>
						<summary><title type="supplied">Book of Hours</title>. <note>The manuscript
								contains texts in several languages: A Calendar of which November
								and December are missing, <title type="uniform">Evangelium Secundum Iohannem</title>, 
								<title type="uniform">The Second Gospel According to John</title>, some prayers and hymns of
								which pp. 231-250 and 333-338 are written in French. Pp.
								167-68 contain a prayer to the Virgin in Italian and on three inserted
								leaves from c. 1700 a description of the manuscript itself, written
								in Latin, is found.</note></summary>
						<msItem n="1">
							<locus from="1r" to="340v">1r-340v</locus>
							<title type="supplied">Book of Hours</title>
